    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Ah, I understand now.\r\n\r\nActually, perhaps you can do it from a startup file. Try making a file `~/.ipython/profile_default/startup/no-ctrl-backslash.py` with contents like this:\r\n\r\n```python\r\nfrom IPython.terminal.shortcuts import force_exit\r\nip.pt_cli.application.key_bindings_registry.remove_binding(force_exit)\r\n```"
