    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks, that is a reasonable workaround, I'll close this issue since it solves the problem I was raising.\r\nCorrect code snippet is the following:\r\n```\r\nfrom IPython.terminal.shortcuts import force_exit\r\nfrom IPython import get_ipython\r\nip = get_ipython()\r\nip.pt_cli.application.key_bindings_registry.remove_binding(force_exit)\r\n```"
